data.description: Old world charm in this 1949 Gate City home. This 3br 1 bath home is located on the corner sitting on 4 city lots which offers privacy the home offers hardwood floors, fireplace in living room which has been closed off because seller does not use. Dining Room and Open Kitchen with updated appliances, including a new refrigerator December 2023. One bedroom on main level and 2 bedrooms on upper level. This home is located in the heart of Gate City which offers  convenience. New Dishwasher, HVAC replaced in 2020, New Plumbing and sewer lines, Ring outdoor cameras, local trash pickup, Lawn service for $45.00 per mow, inside of home has been updated, but may need 4 windows. It also offers a full storage basement  that can be accessed from main area of home with easy access to plumbing and electrical. Lot extends back past trees. The home is in need of new windows and some decking boards in back seller is looking to sell as is.
